1
00:00:13,570 --> 00:00:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There won't be any skilled minions around.</i></font>

2
00:00:17,550 --> 00:00:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They'll all be guarding 
the Coffin Count of Storms.</i></font>

3
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to drag them down here first.</i></font>

4
00:00:24,950 --> 00:00:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara, Jogamine.</font>

5
00:00:27,250 --> 00:00:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to make an exception 
and teach you a fundamental move.</font>

6
00:00:30,380 --> 00:00:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch close.</font>

7
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:40,010
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#4c413a"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="40">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

8
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:09,440
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A Brave's Instruction</b></font></font></font>

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:09,440
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A Brave's Instruction</b></font></font></font>

10
00:02:10,290 --> 00:02:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, here's what you call a bind.</font>

11
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And once you get out of it...</font>

12
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cut off their fingers.</font>

13
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think there's a similar move in 
traditional Japanese kenjutsu, too.</font>

14
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trick is to twist the blade 
once it hits the guard.</font>

15
00:02:39,220 --> 00:02:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once they can't hold a sword,
there's nothing to fear.</font>

16
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you follow, give it a shot.</font>

17
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys take care of the cannon fodder.</font>

18
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood! I'll make an attempt, Master!</font>

19
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You really shouldn't.</i></font>

20
00:03:04,730 --> 00:03:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cutting fingers is a move you attempt 
when you've locked swords with someone.</i></font>

21
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you can read minds,</i></font>

22
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>you oughta get in close by reading 
when they're gonna step forward...</i></font>

23
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nah. That's not possible 
at Jogamine's level.</i></font>

24
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Using that shield to parry while keeping 
an eye out for unprotected vital spots...</i></font>

25
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She has a ways to go before 
she can pull that off, too.</i></font>

26
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:38,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara's moving well enough.</i></font>

27
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess this is how she performs 
when she outclasses the enemy.</i></font>

28
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can tell she was drilled by 
first-rate swordsmen from an early age.</i></font>

29
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nothing like Jogamine.</i></font>

30
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means the problem here...</i></font>

31
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot, go on the offensive!</font>

32
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if he throws you off 
balance, you've got two hands!</font>

33
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fight back! Make the other 
guy realize he could die!</font>

34
00:04:12,070 --> 00:04:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those wide, reckless swings...</i></font>

35
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It should be simple to create 
an opening by fighting back</i></font>

36
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>with the speed a one-handed sword offers.</i></font>

37
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now!</i></font>

38
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the hell are you doing?! Kill him!</i></font>

39
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot!</font>

40
00:04:43,570 --> 00:04:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You stupid asshole!</font>

41
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurts!</font>

42
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well covered.</font>

43
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You picked the perfect 
timing to step in, too.</font>

44
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for you... what the hell was that?</font>

45
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tried to fight as I would
in real combat...</font>

46
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How, exactly?</font>

47
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't ready to kill.</font>

48
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Master, shouldn't a Brave—</font>

49
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Doesn't. Matter.</font>

50
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think this is a game?</font>

51
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I'm not like these murdering scum.</font>

52
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so much fancier and 
respectable." Is that it?</font>

53
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You expect someone else 
to save you every time</font>

54
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and never have to dirty your own hands?</font>

55
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that!</font>

56
00:05:35,810 --> 00:05:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I—</font>

57
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Read my mind.</font>

58
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm furious.</font>

59
00:05:45,350 --> 00:05:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Master...</font>

60
00:05:50,450 --> 00:05:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instructor.</font>

61
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quiet. I'm...</font>

62
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not the point. This idiot...</font>

63
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instructor, look. Who's that?</font>

64
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's a shock.</i></font>

65
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't think...</i></font>

66
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she'd show up in person this soon.</i></font>

67
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems the hundred invitations
I sent you this month have born fruit.</font>

68
00:06:52,050 --> 00:06:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to my party, Yashiro-sama,</font>

69
00:06:56,020 --> 00:07:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and your cadre of strange girls.</font>

70
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bid you the warmest of wishes, 
having joined the festivities.</font>

71
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:11,950
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f1f1f1"><b><font size="28">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

72
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Dark Lord known as the 
Coffin Count of Storms.</i></font>

73
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They say she used to be an executive
 from a yakuza group in Kansai...</i></font>

74
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the details of her 
background are unknown.</i></font>

75
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After the BFE conflict two years ago,</i></font>

76
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she started assimilating orgs 
that had lost their leadership,</i></font>

77
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and before long, she was one of the most 
prominent Dark Lords in the country.</i></font>

78
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I first met her six months ago.</i></font>

79
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was on a gig to kill another Dark Lord 
and just ran into her...</i></font>

80
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't have a lot of options,</i></font>

81
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I killed two or three of her 
minions and got out of there.</i></font>

82
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ever since, she's been
persistent in how...</i></font>

83
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, I guess you'd say
I got her attention?</i></font>

84
00:08:07,890 --> 00:08:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell is she?</font>

85
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is crazy.</font>

86
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You can tell, huh?</font>

87
00:08:14,670 --> 00:08:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's strong?</font>

88
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

89
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I go first?</font>

90
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not fighting her tonight.</font>

91
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the three of you
wouldn't stand a chance.</font>

92
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We wouldn't? Who's stronger, her or you?</font>

93
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Depends on the situation.</font>

94
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you finished chatting 
with your exotic animals?</font>

95
00:08:39,940 --> 00:08:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exotic animals?!</font>

96
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are proud 
students of the academy—</font>

97
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop talking, Jogamine. I'll kick you.</font>

98
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am so honored you accepted 
my invitation, Yashiro-sama.</font>

99
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has the ten million a month I've 
been sending finally paid off?</font>

100
00:08:57,890 --> 00:09:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't show up because of the invite.</font>

101
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to ask you...</font>

102
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, first, I'm gonna complain.</font>

103
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sending all these letters 
and muscle after me...</font>

104
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm obviously not gonna 
use any money you send me!</font>

105
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit trying to launder your 
cash with my account, damn it!</font>

106
00:09:15,090 --> 00:09:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wound me.</font>

107
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My sincere wish is to engage with you</font>

108
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and develop a relationship based on trust.</font>

109
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Pincers not here?</font>

110
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's on leave.</font>

111
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He seems to be worn down from 
the previous day's events...</font>

112
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he will return 
in strength soon enough.</font>

113
00:09:36,130 --> 00:09:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given the support he has.</font>

114
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he told you the details.</font>

115
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking for the Half Dragon.</font>

116
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:53,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you're here regarding your pursuit
of vengeance for Ishino the Musician?</font>

117
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You knew?</font>

118
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. The Half Dragon...</font>

119
00:10:04,490 --> 00:10:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truth of the matter is they've
been a nuisance to me as well.</font>

120
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've been strengthening 
the unruly masses</font>

121
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and attempting to sabotage 
the established order of things.</font>

122
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Basically, they've been making a mess 
of your turf using that E4 stuff, right?</font>

123
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pleased to see you understand.</font>

124
00:10:30,310 --> 00:10:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yashiro-sama, you are no less than 
the ideal swordsman I've dreamed of.</font>

125
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should you join my royal guard,</font>

126
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can unite in our struggles 
against these people.</font>

127
00:10:42,970 --> 00:10:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guarantee you'll be taken care of
 for the rest of your days</font>

128
00:10:45,570 --> 00:10:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the kind of welcome I'd give you.</font>

129
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going nowhere.</font>

130
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not gonna be one of your peons.</font>

131
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to know my nickname, right?</font>

132
00:11:00,190 --> 00:11:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I choose who I kill.</font>

133
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just wanna know where 
to find these people.</font>

134
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the Half Dragon are your enemy,</font>

135
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then we're after the same thing.</font>

136
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I wrong?</font>

137
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but in that scenario,</font>

138
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't be able to enjoy the exploits 
of Yashiro the Reaper with my own eyes.</font>

139
00:11:25,380 --> 00:11:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suppose we do this, then...</font>

140
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four of my most elite 
soldiers, the Stormguard...</font>

141
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you will fight them,</font>

142
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in exchange, I will tell 
you everything I know.</font>

143
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A party needs entertainment, after all.</font>

144
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, given that they're here,</font>

145
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why not have your trio
join the festivities?</font>

146
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold up!</font>

147
00:11:57,130 --> 00:12:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These three are too weak 
to be any entertainment.</font>

148
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my. You seem to actually care 
for this little menagerie, then?</font>

149
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I'm curious about the...</font>

150
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>nature</i> of your relationship.</font>

151
00:12:13,430 --> 00:12:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shit.</i></font>

152
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pairing with Indo to fight 
wouldn't be a problem.</i></font>

153
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if anything happens to Sara,</i></font>

154
00:12:21,830 --> 00:12:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>King Arthur and the Round Table 
will be out for my blood.</i></font>

155
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I have Jogamine read what 
I need to know, and then we bail?</i></font>

156
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. At this point, if I 
don't agree to her offer...</i></font>

157
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It'll just make things even worse.</i></font>

158
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

159
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle down. I'm figuring things out.</font>

160
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that! Above us!</font>

161
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And behind us... we're surrounded!</font>

162
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my, and just when I was 
looking forward to the show.</font>

163
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many visitors today.</font>

164
00:13:21,690 --> 00:13:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Great.</i></font>

165
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I wasn't the only one who thought 
today would be the best day to strike.</i></font>

166
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is such a shame I won't be able to give 
you my undivided attention, Yashiro-sama.</font>

167
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until we meet again...</font>

168
00:14:48,180 --> 00:14:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move!</font>

169
00:15:14,770 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody move without my say.</font>

170
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially you, Jogamine.</font>

171
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's...</i></font>

172
00:15:33,990 --> 00:15:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a Nephilim.</i></font>

173
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Four in the rear.</i></font>

174
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seven flanking us.</i></font>

175
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just getting past them
wouldn't be that hard.</i></font>

176
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do we go after her?</i></font>

177
00:15:56,130 --> 00:15:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If they're after the
Coffin Count of Storms,</i></font>

178
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then the Half Dragon
might be up there, too.</i></font>

179
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukine!</font>

180
00:16:06,610 --> 00:16:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn! Stay close, Sara!</font>

181
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukine! Master's order!</font>

182
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop! Stay put!</font>

183
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid?</font>

184
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What're you doing?</font>

185
00:16:42,330 --> 00:16:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop. Let me go.</font>

186
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What. Are. You. Doing?</font>

187
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those... are Nephilim...</font>

188
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big models, with claws.</font>

189
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara, we have to support Yukine!</font>

190
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take formation!</font>

191
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go!</font>

192
00:17:58,630 --> 00:17:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

193
00:18:13,890 --> 00:18:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it, why can't any of you
do as you're told?</font>

194
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Leg's still intact.</i></font>

195
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Probably five minutes until 
it knits back together.</i></font>

196
00:18:28,330 --> 00:18:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Left leg, left arm...</i></font>

197
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A handicap like that would be bad,
no matter how tough I was.</i></font>

198
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do we do, Sensei?!</font>

199
00:18:40,090 --> 00:18:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your limbs are all screwed up!</font>

200
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We break through!</font>

201
00:18:43,650 --> 00:18:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defending Master as we secure—</font>

202
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knock it off, stupid!</font>

203
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about me for now.</font>

204
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can handle myself.</font>

205
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen!</font>

206
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to adjust your crummy teamwork.</font>

207
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way they were moving 
before made it clear...</i></font>

208
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They've been trained to fight as a trio.</i></font>

209
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Indo goes on the offensive, 
Jogamine backs her up,</i></font>

210
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>while Sara lands the killing blow.</i></font>

211
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's how the academy
taught them to fight.</i></font>

212
00:19:19,970 --> 00:19:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But from what I could see, 
they're not great at it.</i></font>

213
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The academy probably 
wanted to make sure that</i></font>

214
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the Chairman's daughter, Sara, 
was in the safest position.</i></font>

215
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Especially since Indo could take 
out most enemies on her own...</i></font>

216
00:19:36,810 --> 00:19:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And if Indo does go down, 
Jogamine won't be able to make up for it.</i></font>

217
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:45,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All this adds up to Sara not having 
a lot of chances to get involved.</i></font>

218
00:19:46,230 --> 00:19:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a damn joke.</i></font>

219
00:19:48,420 --> 00:19:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to give these three 
effective commands, or I die.</i></font>

220
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to come up with 
something in one second.</i></font>

221
00:19:56,130 --> 00:20:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The best way to capitalize on their 
abilities in a situation like this...</i></font>

222
00:20:04,330 --> 00:20:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

223
00:20:05,990 --> 00:20:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jogamine. You take the lead.</font>

224
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Target their knees 
to put them off balance.</font>

225
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara, you aim for their backs.</font>

226
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't give them a chance to fight back.</font>

227
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you choke and the combo 
falls apart, we all die.</font>

228
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indo, you're to intercept any attacks.</font>

229
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara and Jogamine, back her up.</font>

230
00:20:24,830 --> 00:20:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you screw up, the others will die.</font>

231
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hear me?</font>

232
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need you to bust your butt out there.</font>

233
00:20:33,010 --> 00:20:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you fly off the chain again...</font>

234
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

235
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time... I'll do a good job.</font>

236
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

237
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be an impromptu lesson,</font>

238
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's nice and tense, right?</font>

239
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't pay me any mind.</font>

240
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be seriously pissed off.</font>

241
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, Master...</font>

242
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a live exercise!</font>

243
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get to work!</font>

