248
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:49,910
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="26"><font color="#feffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Next Time</b></font></font></font></font>

249
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The time has come to display 
the power of our friendship!</i></font>

250
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do you three even hang out
outside of school?</i></font>

251
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We learn together, and encourage 
each other to greater heights!</i></font>

252
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time is Episode 11,</i></font>

253
00:22:46,050 --> 00:22:49,910
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>A Brave's Teamwork</b></font></font></font></font>

254
00:22:46,050 --> 00:22:49,910
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>A Brave's Teamwork</b></font></font></font></font>

255
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a "Brave's Teamwork".</i></font>

